Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.03,0:01:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三界層是炎熱的灼熱世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.30,0:01:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配著鐵板村的瑪利亞妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.94,0:01:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她把地面的溫度上升\N令村民受苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.90,0:01:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為地面是鐵板的關係\N真令人受不了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.90,0:01:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏我們得到了\N很重要的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.84,0:01:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,灼熱地獄之迷便藏在\N極寒之劍和灼熱之盾身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.50,0:02:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十三話\N燃燒的鬥魂\N九九八十一攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.14,0:03:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰說可以休息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.58,0:03:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對…對不起,請讓我飲水吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.18,0:03:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水?你口渴了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.68,0:03:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.50,0:03:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?那便特別地\N請你喝這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.77,0:03:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平時一支是要100元的\N我真是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在免費給你喝飲\N怎麼?很高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.81,0:03:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?這麼好喝的東西\N現在可以免費飲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很高興吧?\N來,喝吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.84,0:03:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誠意推推介熔岩飲品,說笑罷\N怎麼?精神了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.76,0:03:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒精神的人\N我隨時也會給他喝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.73,0:03:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,快去工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.09,0:04:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱…我不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.66,0:04:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙到底在想什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水…給我水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.82,0:04:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔,我肚子餓了\N吃熱熱的火鍋鳥東吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.19,0:04:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱,走開啊,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.68,0:04:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃火鍋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.94,0:04:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪,你有水嗎?\N分點給我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.78,0:04:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.32,0:04:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好,全部喝掉了\N真對不起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.40,0:04:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這樣吧,我們是同伴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己一個人喝,真過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.90,0:04:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,這是由我找到的水啊\N這麼想要的話自己去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這樣說話吧\N不是太薄情了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.44,0:05:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼說如果我有困難時\N你們會來救我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.39,0:05:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我說我不要這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.60,0:05:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要恢復原來很有型的男子\N你們會幫我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.72,0:05:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有海的氣味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.89,0:05:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海?在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.70,0:05:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.56,0:05:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很厲害,海在燃燒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.50,0:05:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一片火紅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.01,0:05:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.63,0:05:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個是熱島,因為太過熱\N現在好像沒人住呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.11,0:05:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能極寒之劍和灼熱之盾\N會在那個島上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.50,0:05:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許會在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但怎樣過去呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.96,0:06:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許只有你才能渡過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.80,0:06:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你叫渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點也不好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!那邊有個村\N去看看吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.96,0:06:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我們分頭收集情報吧\N順便找水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.93,0:06:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.32,0:06:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位村民，我今天也帶了\N美味的熔岩飲料來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.26,0:06:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家也好像很想要呢\N好,第一個便是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.69,0:06:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!你想要多少支?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.68,0:06:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?你想要十支?\N是嗎?一支是1000元…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.51,0:06:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是100元嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.25,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼十支是一萬五千元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.30,0:06:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我二萬元嗎?\N好,這裏十支
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.31,0:07:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個…找錢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.69,0:07:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找錢?你說什麼?\N老頭子,一支一千元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十支當然是二萬元了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.42,0:07:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!大叔\N你要多少支熔岩飲料?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.08,0:07:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像在賣果汁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.44,0:07:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了,去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要!我要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.31,0:07:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.70,0:07:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.30,0:07:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個…在下也想要那個飲品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.33,0:07:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?是客人嗎?\N好,想要多少支?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.24,0:07:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要一支便夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.05,0:07:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不客氣了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.50,0:07:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好辣…好辣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.28,0:07:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟喝那不能喝的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能喝的東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.56,0:08:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個叫熔岩飲料的是\N辣得不能喝下的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.58,0:08:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是第三界層的常識啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.60,0:08:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也有點料子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.59,0:08:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要多支
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.30,0:08:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這之前請你先付錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.77,0:08:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?\N大叔你好像在生氣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.91,0:08:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在生氣啊\N我最討厭沒錢的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.40,0:08:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.50,0:08:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.37,0:08:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.54,0:08:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,這大叔不送我果汁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.70,0:08:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡?你便是叫渡的小鬼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.10,0:08:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,竟賣這樣的東西\N還要收錢,太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.93,0:08:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼?\N這個小鬼不是喝得很高興嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,很好喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.61,0:09:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這個雖然是\N火美子是特別的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.05,0:09:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村內的人不是很困惑嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.60,0:09:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口!我已等你好久了\N為了和你決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.18,0:09:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已準備了特別的擂台\N在那處決勝負吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.50,0:09:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可憐…不行呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我接受你挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有骨氣的小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼你放開火美子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.50,0:09:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口,想我放了她的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便把她和那大叔喝的\N熔岩飲料錢交出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.11,0:09:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.21,0:09:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,一支要一千元\N兩支便是三千元了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.92,0:09:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你算錯了吧?一支是一千元\N兩支便是兩千元啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.05,0:09:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?你說我算錯了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連這麼簡單的數\N也算不到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.40,0:09:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口!我從小算數便最差了\N可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我最討厭最近的小鬼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你知道激怒我\N有什麼後果吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.50,0:10:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擂台在我的工廠內\N在比賽前這小鬼放在我這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.28,0:10:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即來啊,工廠啊!\N我在工廠等你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.37,0:10:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.61,0:10:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心\N我很快會來救你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.36,0:10:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.90,0:10:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟激怒馬之介真是個蠢材!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會遇到很慘的事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要連累我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.17,0:10:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣氛好像很奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.17,0:10:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不關我事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.02,0:10:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用你管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.68,0:10:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說得真輕鬆\N激怒那傢伙會這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.19,0:10:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題!\N那樣的傢伙我會收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.40,0:11:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,你說得真好,年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長…長老大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長老大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.50,0:11:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣\N渡從長老大人那處打聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.10,0:11:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包括被迫買工廠運來\N那喝不了的熔岩飲料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.52,0:11:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有極寒之劍\N在那燃燒島上的事也知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.32,0:11:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?\N你便是傳說中的救世主嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是這麼出名嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.75,0:11:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真難為情呢\N要我簽名便糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.60,0:11:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要得意!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.58,0:11:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是長老大人\N要怎樣才能渡過那個島?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.60,0:11:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.75,0:11:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.32,0:11:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘩!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把塞子打開便行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.92,0:11:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塞子是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.96,0:11:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是地下水的塞子\N地點就在地廠的附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它拔出來的話\N地下水便會飛出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直達那島上去成為一條水橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.50,0:12:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水橋嗎?好,師傅\N在我和馬之介比賽時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.75,0:12:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和古拿瑪\N去打開地下的塞子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.35,0:12:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好\N你是要引開馬之介的注意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先說明,那傢伙可是\N專業摔角手中的專業啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.21,0:12:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是在班中摔角第一的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.30,0:12:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我懂得很多招式的\N怎樣啊?混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.58,0:12:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像很強呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.00,0:12:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管來吧,混蛋\N怎樣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.20,0:12:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人注目的一戰\N我是渡對馬之介的旁述多吏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.80,0:12:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天因解說的崎阪先生休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.25,0:12:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以由馬之介先生的人質\N火美子小姐代為解說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比賽開始了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.50,0:13:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在由熔岩商業提供的\N摔角比賽要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.68,0:13:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅方的是重77磅的\N挑戰者戰部渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.33,0:13:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣啊?混蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.75,0:13:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藍方是402磅重的冠軍\N亞普多闌·馬之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟敢來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.50,0:13:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣啊?混蛋,快放了\N火美子和被迫做苦工的村民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.88,0:13:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼大口氣\N在打倒我之後才說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.53,0:13:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來就來吧,你這混蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.53,0:13:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快比賽便會開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.17,0:13:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子小姐\N你對比賽有怎樣的預想?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.02,0:13:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡很有趣很有型!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.87,0:13:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.87,0:13:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,你隨便進攻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.50,0:13:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我來了,你這混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.16,0:14:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!\N那麼我便利用繩索出飛龍腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很癢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這個嗎?好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!\N我叫戰神丸出來破壞它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.01,0:14:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣做的話\N不是立即被人發現嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.83,0:14:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這個…\N戰神丸也打不破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼會知道這種事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個…這是…因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.25,0:14:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.49,0:14:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用什麼特別的工具\N好像打不開啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.00,0:14:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們是不行的了\N回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.30,0:15:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許是這樣呢\N打開塞子時必須的東西是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.02,0:15:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道,很難呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.10,0:15:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是笨鈍的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.50,0:15:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?小鬼\N還未到睡覺的時候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,精神不錯呢,你這混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這樣便不好玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.20,0:15:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!飛起了,飛得很高!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.50,0:15:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.53,0:15:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼簡單就玩完\N會對不起觀眾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他們再多看一會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這小鬼,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.13,0:15:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以\N攻擊其他人是犯規的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.26,0:15:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.42,0:16:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,你等我\N我現在救你出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.63,0:16:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙的弱點…\N要找出他的弱點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,弱點…他的弱點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.40,0:16:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼,因為有人阻止著\N救了你一命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.96,0:16:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這次不會了\N我要再三秒內收拾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.79,0:16:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?\N那不是三啊,是二啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.30,0:16:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是了,我知道你的弱點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.33,0:16:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我哪裏會有弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?那麼這個怎樣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.10,0:16:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!\N九九八十一攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.64,0:16:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.75,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二二得四、二三得六\N三五一十五
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三六一十八、三七二十一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.50,0:16:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.32,0:16:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很怕數學得馬之介\N一聽到九九乘法便會頭痛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.45,0:17:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可憐\N二二得四、二三得六…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很頭痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.86,0:17:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.89,0:17:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,九六五十四、九七六十三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,九八七十二、九九八十一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.83,0:17:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我來了\N渡特級…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛龍踢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.80,0:17:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝利者是渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬歲!萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.85,0:17:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[熔岩金剛]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.77,0:17:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你們嘗嘗這部\N熔岩金剛的特別招式吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.30,0:17:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.78,0:17:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那個了!\N那個便是地下水的開蓋器了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.20,0:17:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,搶那傢伙的開蓋器啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.75,0:18:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開蓋器?好,小蛋\N去拖延著他吧,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什麼傢伙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.62,0:18:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是舒服呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.79,0:18:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.03,0:18:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.09,0:18:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.92,0:19:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,在下也要去電話亭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.40,0:19:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好,我也要去幫他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.95,0:19:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來了嗎?熔岩金剛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.50,0:19:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給他看看你的特別招式\N奪命剪刀腳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.14,0:19:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有什麼大不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.60,0:19:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等,用犯規招式真卑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.24,0:19:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口!\N也讓你嘗嘗我的攻擊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.34,0:19:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!等一等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.20,0:19:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那混蛋,只懂用犯規招式\N不能饒恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.22,0:19:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!龍神丸\N把那傢伙打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.70,0:19:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了嗎?廢魔神,轟天炮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.78,0:19:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不錯呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.86,0:20:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壓下去,龍神丸,不要輸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.56,0:20:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這混蛋,試試這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旋風腿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要放手,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.65,0:20:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作點啊\N戰神丸,站起來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.10,0:20:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,只懂用卑鄙手段\N我不會輸的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.56,0:20:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒頭椿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.79,0:20:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1、2、3…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.27,0:20:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸勝出!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.30,0:20:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.99,0:20:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,囉嗦,還未分勝負呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.64,0:20:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.18,0:20:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.77,0:21:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,登龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.52,0:21:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我記著啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.11,0:21:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!好像來不及了呢\N沒法子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.10,0:21:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是水造的橋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.35,0:21:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要順著這地下水的水流\N便能到達那個島了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.93,0:21:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,出發吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.25,0:21:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.87,0:21:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用飛的過去\N我才不想濕身呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.70,0:22:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多謝你們…

